---
import sopraSrc from "./sopra.jfif";
---

<style>
  .experienceWrapper {
    width: 100%;
    position: relative;

    display: flex;
    flex-direction: row;
    justify-content: space-around;

    margin-top: 6rem;
    padding-bottom: 4rem;
  }

  .card {
    width: 25%;
    background-color: rgb(18, 9, 14);

    padding: 1rem 2rem;

    border-radius: 2rem !important;

    color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.61);

    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;

    align-items: center;

    font-size: 125%;
  }

  .card > h1 {
    text-align: center;
  }

  .card:nth-of-type(1) {
    --neonBorderColor: var(--neonPink);
  }

  .card:nth-of-type(2) {
    --neonBorderColor: var(--neonGreen);
  }

  .card:nth-of-type(3) {
    --neonBorderColor: var(--neonBlue);
  }

  .cardMain {
    margin-top: 1.5rem;
  }

  .htmlDecorators {
    width: 100%;
    height: 100%;
  }

  .htmlDecorators > .topGroup {
    position: absolute;
    top: -3rem;
  }

  .htmlDecorators > .bottomGroup {
    position: absolute;
    bottom: 0;
  }

  @media only screen and (max-width: 1366px) {
    .experienceWrapper {
      flex-direction: column;
    }

    .card {
      padding: 1rem;
      margin: 0 1rem;

      width: 90%;
    }
  }
</style>

<section class="experienceWrapper" id="Experience">
  <section class="card neonBorder">
    <h1 class="neonRed">Sopra Steria Polska</h1>
    <h4 class="neonWhite">Intern</h4>
    <h6>09.2022</h6>
    <p class="cardMain">
      During my final internship experience during school, I was working on
      improving my interpersonal skills as <i><u>First Line Support</u></i> for a
      big international company. My tasks involved providing IT support, troubleshooting
      network switches, and assisting applicants with the use of the <i
        ><u>English language</u></i
      >. Thanks to this opportunity I quickly learned to find solutions while
      working with non-IT individuals and successfully tested my language skills
      in industry, despite initial challenges.
    </p>
  </section>
  <section class="card neonBorder">
    <h1 class="neonGreen">Adient</h1>
    <h5 class="neonWhite">Intern</h5>
  </section>
  <section class="card neonBorder">
    <h1 class="neonBlue">O&amp;S Computer-Soft</h1>
    <h5 class="neonWhite">Intern</h5>
  </section>
  <div class="htmlDecorators">
    <div class="topGroup">
      <pre>
  &lt;section id="Experience"&gt;
    </pre>
    </div>
    <div class="bottomGroup">
      <pre>
  &lt;/section&gt;
    </pre>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
